title: If you think you have this election figured - remember Great Britain
text: The day before Great Britain's election in May, Conservative Leader David Cameron — so uncertain of winning — practiced a resignation speech in front of his inner circle. The next day, he was elected with a majority. Are there echoes in the UK election for Canadians? ...
